articles.title: Police in Australia ID Tanya Lee Glover as body found in concrete wall - USA TODAY
articles.description: Queensland Police said skeletal remains buried in the wall of a Brisbane apartment belong to Tanya Lee Glover, likely slain about 12 years ago.
